object.customQuery:
select distinct
tg.groups_number as Agency_Group_Nbr,
CASE
    WHEN TRIM(BOTH ' ' FROM CONCAT(gw.contingent_group_name1,gw.contingent_group_name2)) IS NULL OR
LEN(TRIM (BOTH ' ' FROM CONCAT(gw.contingent_group_name1,gw.contingent_group_name2)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE 
TRIM(BOTH ' ' FROM concat(gw.contingent_group_name1,gw.contingent_group_name2)) end as Agency_Group_Name,
case when ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name1)) is null or len(ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name1)))=0 then null else ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name1)) end as Agency_Group_Name1
,case when ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name2)) is null or len(ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name2)))=0 then null else ltrim(rtrim(gw.contingent_group_name2)) end as Agency_Group_Name2
,gw.qualifyingamount as Qualifying_Amount
,ltrim(rtrim(dd.name)) as FieldRepresentative_Name
,ltrim(rtrim(gw.fieldrep)) as SalesTerritoryDesc
,gw.fieldrep_state as FieldRepresentativeState
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)) END  as Agency_Email1
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)) END  as Agency_Email2
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)) END  as Agency_Email3
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)) END  as Agency_Email4
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)) END  as Agency_Email5
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)) END  as Agency_Email6
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)) END  as Agency_Email7
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)) END  as Agency_Email8
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)) END  as Agency_Email9
,CASE WHEN LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)) IS NULL OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)))=0 THEN NULL ELSE LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)) END  as Agency_Email10
from  dbo.Groups_stg tg (nolock)
left join dbo.GroupGuidewire_Stg gw (nolock) on gw.groups_nup = tg.groups_nup
left join dbo.fieldreps_stg dd (nolock) on gw.fieldrep = dd.id
left join dbo.AgencyEmail_stg ae (nolock) on tg.groups_nup=ae.group_nup
ORDER BY tg.groups_number  ----
